summary: I am an Industrial Designer specialising in user experience and brand design. After receiving my Bachelor degree in the Netherlands, I currently reside in Prague, Czech Republic. With my work I aim to design subtle products which would enhance user's lives. Within my projects I implement design methodology, with iterative thinking and thorough experimental research. In my experience I worked on both digital and physical products, but I particularly enjoy bringing the two disciplines together.
